title: The Brand Isn’t Magic
author: VD
content_html:
FedEx’s second-ever CEO in its history, Raj Subranamiam, has hired two new Executive Vice-Presidents, Vishal Talwar and Kawal Preet.

Better consider alternative shipping options before it’s too late.
